      "raw_text": "Steve Adams, according to At\ntorney Fred Miller, counsel for the\nWestern Federation of Miners, may\nnot be taken to Colorado. He\nstated this morning that motion\nwill be heard at RatnGrum, Idaho,\nDec. 27 to take Adams to Colorado,\nbut Idaho officers are understood\nto want to keep Adams and try him\non a charge of numbering man\nnamed Boule, who disappeared\nabout the same time as Tyler, for\nwhose murder he was twice tried\nwith the jury disagreeing each\ntime,"
    }
